<taxonomicName authorityName="Dohrn" authorityYear="1859" lsidName="" pageId="0" pageNumber="49" rank="tribe" tribe="Coelidiini">Coelidiini</taxonomicName>
by the aedeagus having two medial or apical to subapical processes glabrous or with multi-spinose or multi-setose secondary processes (
